<div id="c35">
<p>A lot of this is obvious.  Is the person likable?  Do they seem smart and do their answers make sense?  Are they &#8220;learners&#8221;?  Will this person drive me crazy after a month?</p>

<p>Other things like working on small projects for me or temporary evaluation assignments don&#8217;t scale well - at least not any large company that I&#8217;ve ever worked for.</p>

